oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hales Bar Lock and Dam
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph showing the tunnel underneath Hales Bar Lock and Dam. The Chattanooga and Tennessee River Power Company began building the dam on October 17, 1905 and completed it on November 11, 1913. The dam ceased operation on December 14, 1967.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Dams; Tunnels
